@sportstensor・41 

## Congratulations miners!
Due to the efforts of your model development and trainings, in just 5 weeks we've closed in on the benchmark accuracy and according to our trajectory, should be surpassing it consistently in a week or two.

## New Dashboard, who dis?
https://dashboard.sportstensor.com/
- A grand redesign of our dashboard is here! More information, more colours, more everything! :partyfast: 
- Prediction accuracy time-series graph to show how we're progressing as a subnet
- Leaderboard now packed with more data for each miner such as historic prediction accuracy, age and recent matches

## Incentive mechanism rework!
The ultimate goal of Sportstensor is to foster healthy competition between miners and incentivize them to improve on their models and prediction accuracy. While only being a month old, we believe improvements can be made to increase competition.

What exacerbates the issue is that our base model is perhaps *too good* which leaves miners complacent with it's performance.

**Fear not!** the Sportstensor team has recently been joined by a published researcher to collaborate on designing an incentive mechanism that will set this subnet up for long-term future success and to disrupt many industries. The idea is to reward *unique* and *consistent* accuracy through a Pareto Distribution. More information to come!

## Two weeks out - NFL
- The NFL model will be released on the 5th September, however requests will begin on the 3rd.
- A base model will be provided but we encourage everyone to start developing their own NFL model asap 😉
- To coincide with the start of the NFL season, **we'll launch our frontend dapp at the same time** :yipee:
